data.description: EAGLEWOOD(3640G)- Spring has Sprung so now it is time for Summer FUN!! This absolutely adorable 3 bedroom, 2 full baths, 1 car garage home is located on a large, large lot, all while nestled in the heart of Hope Mills! Open concept feel with the living, dining and kitchen. Renovated in 2020 to include roof, windows, vinyl plank flooring (except bedrooms), granite countertop, stainless steel kitchen appliances, light fixtures, and water heater. Relax on the deck or grill on the patio while visualizing your desires in the large back yard, plenty of room for gardening, playing, and/or creating that private oasis you may be dreaming of! Home and carpets will be professionally cleaned for you when making this your new home! Close to parks, trails, library, schools, shopping, dining, Hope Mills Lake. Did you know you can swim and kayak in Hope Mills Lake? Talk about some summer fun! So come on over and make this your new home TODAY!
